{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-post-contentful-moztiq-blog-slug-tsx","path":"/post/generate-newyearcard-chatgpt/","result":{"data":{"contentfulMoztiqBlog":{"id":"113d887d-63a2-5a4d-b0ba-80281226bf5f","title":"연하장 만들기 (feat. ChatGPT)","slug":"generate-newyearcard-chatgpt","category":"ai","releaseDate":"2023-12-28T00:00+09:00","headerImage":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/vpyfljks33op/3j1bjeAUKTihNsKLweY88K/dcd3d265147e09c113eb76ef4acf6c8a/modified_korean_ink_painting_with_text.png"},"contents":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>출처 : <a href=\"https://jehyunlee.github.io/2023/12/25/General-33-ChatGPT_DataAnalysis/\">ChatGPT로 한글과 한자가 적힌 카드 만들기</a></p>\n<p>Chat GPT 를 활용해 연하장(새해 인사가 들어간 이미지)을 만드는 기술블로그의 포스팅을 보고 저도 한번 똑같이 따라해봤습니다. 역시 전문가들은 시도 자체가 다르군요. 존경합니다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>첫번째 프롬프트를 전달합니다.\n<strong>Use Dall.E: draw korean ink painting style landscape image, sephia tone, minimalism</strong>\n<img src=\"//images.ctfassets.net/vpyfljks33op/7mKpS0iXeDGI2jext3zpVU/a9b38c3b41d87bb311aa46c7a30f5bfa/DALL_E_2023-12-28_18.27.08_-_A_minimalist_Korean_ink_painting_style_landscape__rendered_in_sepia_tones._The_composition_shou.png\" alt=\"DALL·E 2023-12-28 18.27.08 - A minimalist Korean ink painting style landscape, rendered in sepia tones. The composition should be sparse, emphasizing the elegance of empty space,\"></p>\n<p>조선일보에서 제공하는 조선100년체 폰트를 파일로 첨부하며 두번째 프롬프트를 전달합니다. 몇 번 분석실패하더니 아래와 같은 결과를 냅니다.\n<strong>Use Data Analysis: add text '새해 복 많이 받으세요' on top 20% of the generated image above in black, center in horizontal alignment. use the attached font.</strong>\n<img src=\"//images.ctfassets.net/vpyfljks33op/3j1bjeAUKTihNsKLweY88K/dcd3d265147e09c113eb76ef4acf6c8a/modified_korean_ink_painting_with_text.png\" alt=\"modified korean ink painting with text\"></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>아래는 ChatGPT가 데이터 분석에 사용한 코드입니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-python line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># Text to be added</span>\ntext <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"새해 복 많이 받으세요\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Reopen the image</span>\nimage <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Image<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>image_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Setup font and calculate text size and position</span>\nfont_size <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">60</span>\nfont <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ImageFont<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>truetype<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>font_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> font_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\ndraw <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ImageDraw<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Draw<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>image<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\ntext_width<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> text_height <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> draw<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textsize<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> font<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>font<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nimage_width<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> image_height <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> image<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>size\nx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>image_width <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> text_width<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span>\ny <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> image_height <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.1</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 10% from the top</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Add text to the image</span>\ndraw<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> text<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> font<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>font<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> fill<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"black\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Save the modified image</span>\nmodified_image_path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/mnt/data/modified_korean_ink_painting_with_text.png'</span>\nimage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>save<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>modified_image_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nmodified_image_path</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>Dall.E 에게 한글과 관련한 요청을 하면 제대로 표시하지 못하는 문제가 있었는데 이런 식으로 처리할 수도 있군요. 신기한 녀석입니다.</p>","tableOfContents":"","excerpt":"출처 : ChatGPT로 한글과 한자가 적힌 카드 만들기 Chat GPT…"}},"tag":["ChatGPT","연하장"]}},"pageContext":{"id":"113d887d-63a2-5a4d-b0ba-80281226bf5f","slug":"generate-newyearcard-chatgpt","__params":{"slug":"generate-newyearcard-chatgpt"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3507440187"],"slicesMap":{}}